PwsPHP v1.2.2 Final - Multiples vulnerabilities
-----------------------------------------------

VULNERABLE PRODUCT
------------------
Forum: Pwsphp
Version: 1.2.2 Final
Vulnerabilities: Multiples
--------------------------

